{"info": {"author": "codeif", "author_email": "me@codeif.com", "bugtrack_url": null, "classifiers": ["Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "description": "Flask-WX-OAuth\n==============\n\n.. inclusion-marker-do-not-remove\n\n\u5b98\u65b9\u6587\u6863\n----------\n\n- `\u5fae\u4fe1\u7f51\u9875\u6388\u6743 <https://mp.weixin.qq.com/wiki?t=resource/res_main&id=mp1421140842>`_\n\n- `\u6388\u6743\u540e\u63a5\u53e3\u8c03\u7528 <https://open.weixin.qq.com/cgi-bin/showdocument?action=dir_list&t=resource/res_list&verify=1&id=open1419316518&lang=zh_CN>`_\n\n- `\u516c\u4f17\u5e73\u53f0\u6d4b\u8bd5\u8d26\u53f7 <http://mp.weixin.qq.com/debug/cgi-bin/sandbox?t=sandbox/login>`_\n\n\u5b89\u88c5\n-------\n\n.. code-block:: sh\n\n    pip install Flask-WX-OAuth\n\n\u4f7f\u7528\u65b9\u5f0f\n----------\n\nflask\u6269\u5c55\u7684\u4f7f\u7528\u65b9\u5f0f:\n\n.. code-block:: python\n\n    from flask_wx_oauth import WXOAuth\n\n    wx_oauth = WXOAuth()\n    wx_oauth.init_app(app)\n\n\n\n\u4e5f\u53ef\u4ee5\u6bcf\u6b21\u521d\u59cb\u5316\u540e\u4f7f\u7528:\n\n.. code-block:: python\n\n    from flask_wx_oauth import WXOAuth\n    wx_oauth = WXOAuth(appid='YOUR APPID', secret='YOUR SECRET')\n\n\n\u5728view\u4e2d\u8c03\u7528\n--------------\n\n.. code-block:: py\n\n    next = request.args.get('next', '/')\n    redirect_uri = url_for('.authorized', next=next, _external=True)\n    params = dict(\n        redirect_uri=redirect_uri,\n        scope='snsapi_base',\n    )\n    return redirect(wx_oauth.get_authorize_url(**params))\n\n\n\u8fd0\u884c\u793a\u4f8b\u4ee3\u7801\n--------------\n\n.. code-block:: sh\n\n    docker build -t flask-wx-oauth .\n    docker run -v $(pwd):/app -p 5000:5000 flask-wx-oauth", "description_content_type": "", "docs_url": null, "download_url": "", "downloads": {"last_day": -1, "last_month": -1, "last_week": -1}, "home_page": "https://github.com/codeif/Flask-WX-OAuth", "keywords": "", "license": "MIT", "maintainer": "", "maintainer_email": "", "name": "Flask-WX-OAuth", "package_url": "https://pypi.org/project/Flask-WX-OAuth/", "platform": "", "project_url": "https://pypi.org/project/Flask-WX-OAuth/", "project_urls": {"Documentation": "https://flask-wx-oauth.readthedocs.io", "Homepage": "https://github.com/codeif/Flask-WX-OAuth"}, "release_url": "https://pypi.org/project/Flask-WX-OAuth/0.2.3/", "requires_dist": null, "requires_python": "", "summary": "Flask Extension for wechat oauth2.0.", "version": "0.2.3", "yanked": false, "html_description": "<div class=\"project-description\">\n            <div id=\"id1\">\n<h2>\u5b98\u65b9\u6587\u6863</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/wiki?t=resource/res_main&amp;id=mp1421140842\" rel=\"nofollow\">\u5fae\u4fe1\u7f51\u9875\u6388\u6743</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://open.weixin.qq.com/cgi-bin/showdocument?action=dir_list&amp;t=resource/res_list&amp;verify=1&amp;id=open1419316518&amp;lang=zh_CN\" rel=\"nofollow\">\u6388\u6743\u540e\u63a5\u53e3\u8c03\u7528</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/debug/cgi-bin/sandbox?t=sandbox/login\" rel=\"nofollow\">\u516c\u4f17\u5e73\u53f0\u6d4b\u8bd5\u8d26\u53f7</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div id=\"id5\">\n<h2>\u5b89\u88c5</h2>\n<pre>pip install Flask-WX-OAuth\n</pre>\n</div>\n<div id=\"id6\">\n<h2>\u4f7f\u7528\u65b9\u5f0f</h2>\n<p>flask\u6269\u5c55\u7684\u4f7f\u7528\u65b9\u5f0f:</p>\n<pre><span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">flask_wx_oauth</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">WXOAuth</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">wx_oauth</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">WXOAuth</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n<span class=\"n\">wx_oauth</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">init_app</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">app</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</pre>\n<p>\u4e5f\u53ef\u4ee5\u6bcf\u6b21\u521d\u59cb\u5316\u540e\u4f7f\u7528:</p>\n<pre><span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">flask_wx_oauth</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">WXOAuth</span>\n<span class=\"n\">wx_oauth</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">WXOAuth</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">appid</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'YOUR APPID'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">secret</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'YOUR SECRET'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</pre>\n</div>\n<div id=\"view\">\n<h2>\u5728view\u4e2d\u8c03\u7528</h2>\n<pre><span class=\"nb\">next</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">request</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">args</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">get</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'next'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'/'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">redirect_uri</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">url_for</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'.authorized'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"nb\">next</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"nb\">next</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">_external</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"kc\">True</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">params</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">dict</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">redirect_uri</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">redirect_uri</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">scope</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'snsapi_base'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"k\">return</span> <span class=\"n\">redirect</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">wx_oauth</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">get_authorize_url</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">**</span><span class=\"n\">params</span><span class=\"p\">))</span>\n</pre>\n</div>\n<div id=\"id7\">\n<h2>\u8fd0\u884c\u793a\u4f8b\u4ee3\u7801</h2>\n<pre>docker build -t flask-wx-oauth .\ndocker run -v <span class=\"k\">$(</span><span class=\"nb\">pwd</span><span class=\"k\">)</span>:/app -p <span class=\"m\">5000</span>:5000 flask-wx-oauth\n</pre>\n</div>\n\n          </div>"}, "last_serial": 6240234, "releases": {"0.1.1": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "ad2d2d7e9a695b2320bc040b90fed496", "sha256": "700af7a252e54d4392b7e05f924d92dc2197e413d8810785ddb5265f4c1e1a40"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "Flask-WX-OAuth-0.1.1.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "ad2d2d7e9a695b2320bc040b90fed496", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": null, "size": 3362, "upload_time": "2017-04-21T11:03:12", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2017-04-21T11:03:12.887724Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/6b/d7/42fdb2f184fd84abcf3aba465916657fccfa4b8bd9516b13d90c69305824/Flask-WX-OAuth-0.1.1.tar.gz", "yanked": false}], "0.1.2": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "2737e46922778a0ebbf29d99f35253b0", "sha256": "0e3d65e16774f9f9dd46baf2c5a1c64641a29db8f0792199b041d8d2073b0495"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "Flask-WX-OAuth-0.1.2.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "2737e46922778a0ebbf29d99f35253b0", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": null, "size": 3596, "upload_time": "2018-12-04T10:43:03", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2018-12-04T10:43:03.700897Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/53/60/fed0b3660062266f2f990a35c3426d373b5b648e666b8872e8e4989ddd52/Flask-WX-OAuth-0.1.2.tar.gz", "yanked": false}], "0.1.3": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "a91c3ac15dd6e20b413d960c8ff2a55d", "sha256": "2c1b68c937d687348f68e531f17b44ddb48c4ec86b79425f9f40283fda6b8313"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "Flask-WX-OAuth-0.1.3.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "a91c3ac15dd6e20b413d960c8ff2a55d", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": null, "size": 3625, "upload_time": "2018-12-04T10:46:33", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2018-1